  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hiding.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that was in January, 1943.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in January, as I said, all that period from September on, the ghetto was, as I said, not anymore a continuous living area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were only those areas where the shops were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those were the areas where people worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were on the street outside mostly in the morning when they were to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the evening, when they went back to the home, if one can say home, to their apartments, or places where they lived.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was some-- they walked a bit around in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those terrains-- those areas of the shops were really kind of labor camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That really was already a bit of a very much a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in January, there was this action.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, again, there was a period of relative quiet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we already must have-- my family must have planned before that the hope of salvation is in going on to the what was called Aryan side, Polish side, of Warsaw, and hiding, or getting false papers, or hiding otherwise, pretending that one was Polish, and leaving the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was what-- I think that many, many people came to the same conclusion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all through that period, people were living, and leaving the ghetto, and obtaining false papers, and looking for a place to hide on the-- in the Aryan quarter of Warsaw, in the Aryan area of Warsaw, which was, of course, the whole of the city, except for the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was a very hard decision, because although people were terribly afraid of staying in the ghetto, they were as well very much afraid of going to the Aryan side.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
